Subject: Re: [T2] generator light....




> If the brushes are wearing out that fast I would suspect the armature is worn
> roughly from the old brushes. The best way to repair is to disassemble the
> generator and torn the armature on a lathe to true up the contact surface. In a
> pinch I've disassembled and used crocus cloth on the contact surface. Make sure
> everything is clean before you reassemble with new brushes. Hope this helps.
> Tom
>
